  4→ * Extends observer-test-kit and intent-test-kit with helpers
  5→ * for testing LLM reasoning persistence on observations and intents.
  6→ *
  7→ * Driving ports:
  8→ *   createObservation()          — observation query function
  9→ *   updateIntentStatus()         — intent query function
 10→ *   POST /api/intents/:id/evaluate  — intent evaluation endpoint
 11→ *   GET /api/workspaces/:ws/observer/observations — observation list API
